    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Bacteroidetes/Firmicutes ratio\"\nauthor:\n  - name: Muluh\n---\n\n\n\n\n## Bacteroidetes/Firmicutes ratio\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n\n### Group-wise comparisons\n\n-   **Taxonomic level:** Phylum\n-   **Group variable:** diet\n-   **Multiple testing correction:** fdr\n-   **Statistical test** Wilcoxon\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ratio_files/figure-html/visualize-plot-1.png){fig-align='center' width=480}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n\n#### Table of the top findings\n\n#### Across-group\n\n##### Before treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **fdr**\n-   Statistical test: **Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-4a4b785abb16133f9cbd\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-4a4b785abb16133f9cbd\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of  Bacteroidetes/Firmicutes before Treatment<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"rice\"],[\"oat\"],[0.29],[0.32],[0.12],[0.41]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>group1<\\/th>\\n      <th>group2<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.adj<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data